    "description": { "zh-Hans": "应用遮罩、亮度转 Alpha、反转 Alpha，以及预乘或反预乘颜色。", "en": "Apply masks, convert luminance to alpha, invert alpha, and pre/unpremultiply colors." },
    "tags": ["alpha", "transparency", "mask"], "author": "BuiltIn", "version": "1.0"
